0bb2193777b619139b53b43279ff0be4f4cc75ed_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"shopify","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":2006529,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi @sijad, exploiting this required the permission “manage users” which effectively allows users to invite anyone and grant permissions for the invited account when doing so. Effectively, someone with manage users could grant themselves the same permissions as the owner so the impact of this XSS was minimal in comparison. In contrast, #263876 would have allowed a regular user to target an administrator.\n\nHope that helps clarify things.\nPete","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eHi \u003ca href=\"/sijad\"\u003e@sijad\u003c/a\u003e, exploiting this required the permission “manage users” which effectively allows users to invite anyone and grant permissions for the invited account when doing so. Effectively, someone with manage users could grant themselves the same permissions as the owner so the impact of this XSS was minimal in comparison. In contrast, \u003ca href=\"/reports/263876\"\u003e#263876\u003c/a\u003e would have allowed a regular user to target an administrator.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHope that helps clarify things.\u003cbr\u003e\nPete\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-09-19T17:33:24.410Z","updated_at":"2017-09-19T17:33:24.410Z","actor":{"username":"shopify-peteryaworski","cleared":false,"url":"/shopify-peteryaworski","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/175/526/7ba4844078e290c91c4c46a345b4f9e7666f3ed4_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"shopify","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":2006553,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"thanks for clarification and thanks again for bounty. as I can see, admin privileges was needed to trigger #263876, an admin user with Navigation access only have access to that area.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003ethanks for clarification and thanks again for bounty. as I can see, admin privileges was needed to trigger \u003ca href=\"/reports/263876\"\u003e#263876\u003c/a\u003e, an admin user with Navigation access only have access to that area.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-09-19T17:41:26.906Z","updated_at":"2017-09-19T17:41:26.906Z","actor":{"username":"coldd","cleared":false,"url":"/coldd","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/008/745/0bb2193777b619139b53b43279ff0be4f4cc75ed_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"shopify","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":2006619,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi @sijad, sorry for not being entirely clear. In your report, you effectively are already able to perform all administrative actions since you need the `manage users` permission and can already create administrator accounts. In #263876, a user with just the navigation privilege can exploit that XSS vulnerability. In doing so, it's possible they may be able compromise the administrator's account and perform actions that don't have permission to access given they only have navigation privileges to begin with.\n\nIn essence, your XSS was admin -\u003e admin, whereas #263876 the XSS was user -\u003e admin.\n\nHope thats a little more clear.\nPete","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eHi \u003ca href=\"/sijad\"\u003e@sijad\u003c/a\u003e, sorry for not being entirely clear. In your report, you effectively are already able to perform all administrative actions since you need the \u003ccode\u003emanage users\u003c/code\u003e permission and can already create administrator accounts. In \u003ca href=\"/reports/263876\"\u003e#263876\u003c/a\u003e, a user with just the navigation privilege can exploit that XSS vulnerability. In doing so, it\u0026#39;s possible they may be able compromise the administrator\u0026#39;s account and perform actions that don\u0026#39;t have permission to access given they only have navigation privileges to begin with.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn essence, your XSS was admin -\u0026gt; admin, whereas \u003ca href=\"/reports/263876\"\u003e#263876\u003c/a\u003e the XSS was user -\u0026gt; admin.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHope thats a little more clear.\u003cbr\u003e\nPete\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-09-19T18:00:33.782Z","updated_at":"2017-09-19T18:00:33.782Z","actor":{"username":"shopify-peteryaworski","cleared":false,"url":"/shopify-peteryaworski","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/175/526/7ba4844078e290c91c4c46a345b4f9e7666f3ed4_original.jpg/eb31823a4cc9f6b6bb4db930ffdf512533928a68a4255fb50a83180281a60da5"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"shopify","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":2006648,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"that makes sense, thanks again for clarification.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003ethat makes sense, thanks again for clarification.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-09-19T18:06:40.079Z","updated_at":"2017-09-19T18:06:40.079Z","actor":{"username":"coldd","cleared":false,"url":"/coldd","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/0